sub_title: Operations manager with a strong customer focus
summary:
As a professional manager I like to facilitate and coach my team with a commercial focus. I like to apply my knowledge and experience in a technical engineer to order environment. Based on my broadly oriented background I like to connect disciplines and listen to the voice of the customer. 

Furthermore I am a strong believer in Continuous Improvement and I am recognized as a certified Lean Sigma Black Belt for Industries. I like to take responsibility and focus on quality, delivery and costs.
